#### PAM
Pluggable Authentication Modules - a lib for authentication functions...

> ldd /usr/bin/passwd | grep libpam     ldd prints shared object dependencies
                                            shows which cmd use PAM lib


### NSS
Name Service Switch - decide which sources will be used for User, Groups, Hosts.
Normaly for login the files are located unter /etc/passwd [...] NSS manages
this access to the files. 
/etc/nsswitch.conf

### NSCD
Name Service Caching Daemon - Well, a cach for name requests